Package: ILAMM
Type: Package
Title: Non-convex Regularized Robust Regression with I-LAMM Algorithm
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Xiaoou Pan, Qiang Sun, Wen-Xin Zhou
Maintainer: Xiaoou Pan <xip024@ucsd.edu>, 
    Qiang Sun <qsun@utstat.toronto.edu>, 
    Wen-Xin Zhou <wez243@ucsd.edu>
Description: A C++ implementation of I-LAMM algorithm to non-convex regularized regression and non-convex regularized Huber regression, where non-convex penalties include Lasso, smoothly clipped absolute deviation (SCAD) and minimax concave penalty (MCP). Tuning parameters lambda (for penalty) and tau (for Huber loss) can be either user-specified or determined by k-folds cross validation. Other options include adding an intercept term into the model and modifying parameters in the I-LAMM algorithm.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
